PARAM_SIMPLE - Static variable in class com.box.androidlib.Box
Parameter for getAccountTree() indicating that only a limited set of attributes should be returned to make for smaller, more efficient output (folders only contain the 'name' and 'id' attributes, and files will contain the 'name', 'id', 'created', and 'size' attributes).
